tags=system.tag.browse(filter={"tagType":"Provider"}).results
	arrTagProviders=[]
	for result in tags:
		provider=str(result['fullPath'])
		if provider != "[System]":
			arrTagProviders.append(provider)
	return arrTagProviders

config.script:
fileBytes = event.file.getBytes()
	data = Standard.Utilities.Excel.ExcelToList(bytesIn = fileBytes,hasHeaders = True)
	i=1
	for row in data:
		row['localID'] = i
		i = i+1
	self.custom.data = data

modelTagPaths = self.parent.getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("Table").props.data
	modelItemTagPath = self.view.custom.modelItemPath
	collisionPolicy = self.view.custom.collisionPolicy
	modelItemName = self.view.custom.modelItem
	tagProviderName = self.view.custom.tagProvider
	
	tagProvider = "["+tagProviderName+"]"
	modelItemTagPath = tagProvider + "_types_/" + modelItemTagPath
	
	for modelTagPath in modelTagPaths:
		baseTagPath = tagProvider + modelTagPath['Model Path']
		tagName = modelItemName
		typeId = modelItemTagPath
		tagType = "UdtInstance"
		collisionPolicy = collisionPolicy
		tag = {
				"name": tagName,         
				"typeId" : typeId,
				"tagType" : tagType
				,"parameters" : {}
			   }
		system.tag.configure(baseTagPath, [tag], collisionPolicy)

transforms.code:
modelTagPaths = self.parent.getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("Table").props.data
	modelItemTagPath = self.view.custom.modelItemPath
	collisionPolicy = self.view.custom.collisionPolicy
	modelItemName = self.view.custom.modelItem
	tagProviderName = self.view.custom.tagProvider
	
	tagProvider = "["+tagProviderName+"]"
	modelItemTagPath = tagProvider + "_types_/" + modelItemTagPath
	tags = []
	for modelTagPath in modelTagPaths:
		baseTagPath = tagProvider + modelTagPath['Model Path']
		tagName = modelItemName
		typeId = modelItemTagPath
		tagType = "UdtInstance"
		collisionPolicy = collisionPolicy
		tag = {
				"name": tagName,         
				"typeId" : typeId,
				"tagType" : tagType
				,"parameters" : {}
			   }
		tags.append(tag)
	return tags
